Name: AUTH
Flags: Fast, Loading, NoAuth, NoScript, Stale, AllowBusy

KeySpecifications.Notes: This command allows both access and modification of the key
We cannot tell how the keys will be used so we assume the worst, RW and UPDATE
RW and UPDATE because it changes the TTL

Name: HELLO
Flags: Fast, Loading, NoAuth, NoScript, Stale, AllowBusy

KeySpecifications.Notes: RW because it may change the internal representation of the key, and propagate to replicas

Name: QUIT
Flags: Fast, Loading, NoAuth, NoScript, Stale, AllowBusy

KeySpecifications.Notes: RW and ACCESS due to the optional `GET` argument
